      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IMPRESS JOE (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from Cadillac Girl in third (17.97) at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Makes plenty of appeal. CADILLAC MAGIC (2) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 7 length fifth (18.47) at this track in a Other. May be worth another try. CADILLAC LLOYD (8) was a course and distance placegetter (18.19) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 4 length third in a Other. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Should be in this for a long way. SHE'S FIRED UP (4) is another with top-three prospects.",
